Class EventCause

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team6.project.entities.EventCause
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class EventCause
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class creates an Entity called EventCause which implements Serializable and uses the composite key called EventCausePK.

    It creates 3 columns called causeCode , eventId , and description

    Cristiana Conti
